# Server-only resume processing

- PDF/DOCX parsing (`extractText`, `pdf-parse`, `mammoth`) runs in `server/` only.
- Gemini calls only in `server/utils/geminiParse.ts` via `runtimeConfig.geminiApiKey`.
- Client uploads via `multipart` to `POST /api/parse`; receives structured fields, not full extracted text by default.

Do not add client-side Gemini keys or send full resume text to third parties from the browser.
